OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 30 Jul to Thu 13 Aug
OL,6,FPerhaps a somewhat more changeable
OL,7,Fperiod, with the potential for showers
OL,8,For thunderstorms or even some longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain at times. Drier and
OL,10,Fbrighter interludes are also likely,
OL,11,Fperhaps more likely across the south
OL,12,Fand southeast. Temperatures are likely
OL,13,Fto be above normal with some hot
OL,14,Fspells possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
